Source: libcfitsio3
Section: Development/Libraries
Priority: extra
Maintainer: Jasem Mutlaq <mutlaqja@ikarustech.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper (>= 5)
Standards-Version: 3.7.2

Package: libcfitsio3
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CFITSIO is a library of C and Fortran subroutines for reading and writing data files in FITS (Flexible Image Transport System) data format. CFITSIO provides simple high-level routines for reading and writing FITS files that insulate the programmer from the internal complexities of the FITS format. CFITSIO also provides many advanced features for manipulating and filtering the information in FITS files.

Package: libcfitsio3-dev
Architecture: any
Depends: libcfitsio3, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Description: CFITSIO is a library of C and Fortran subroutines for reading and writing data files in FITS (Flexible Image Transport System) data format. CFITSIO provides simple high-level routines for reading and writing FITS files that insulate the programmer from the internal complexities of the FITS format. CFITSIO also provides many advanced features for manipulating and filtering the information in FITS files. This package provides development headers for libcfitsio
